title: 2008 French Football League Championship Game
description:
2008 French Football League Championship Game.

La Courneuve Flash vs Elancourt Templiers

Played the 06.28.2008 in Paris, France, Charlety Stadium.
15000 spectators.

14th Diamond Helmet.
Historical one:
The Flash could win his 4th title in a row (1st team to do so in french football history) or the Templiers could win there 1st title ever.

In regular season, the Templiers beat the Flash and ended a 40 game winning streak.
